   <body>
      <p>The forks can be moved right or left by pulling backwards or
pushing forwards on this lever. The moving speed can be controlled
by tilt angle of the lever and accelerator pedal effort.</p>
      <p>When the lever is pushed forward with the switch on the handle
pressed down, left/right forks move towards left maintaining the
same fork width.</p>
      <p>When the lever is pulled backward with the switch on the handle
pressed down, left/right forks move towards right maintaining the
same fork width.</p>
      <p>To reset the side shift function, release the switch on the
handle.</p>
